Bug Map Code

icon <- makeIcon(
  iconUrl = "ladybug.png",
  iconWidth = 35,
  iconHeight = 35
)

#make an interactive map
leaflet(data = bug_points) %>%
   addProviderTiles(providers$OpenStreetMap, group = "Satellite") %>%
   addProviderTiles(providers$Esri.WorldImagery, group = "Road Map") %>%
  addMarkers(
    lng = ~Longitude,
    lat = ~Latitude,
    icon = ~icon,
    popup = ~popup_html
)%>%
  addLayersControl(
    baseGroups = c("Road Map", "Satellite"),
    options = layersControlOptions(collapsed = FALSE)
)%>%
    addScaleBar(position = "bottomleft") %>%
    addLayersControl(
    baseGroups = c("Road Map", "Satellite"),
    options = layersControlOptions(collapsed = FALSE)
)

ggplot(bug_points, aes(x = Longitude, y = Latitude, color = Color )) +
  geom_point(size = 3, alpha = 0.8) +
  scale_color_manual(values = c(
    "Red" = "red",

    "Orange" = "orange",

    "Black" = "black"
  )) +

anova <- aov(Latitude ~ Color, bug_points)
summary(anova)
